public class AbiquoTemplateOptions
extends org.jclouds.compute.options.TemplateOptions
implements Cloneable

Contains options supported by the ComputeService.createNodesInGroup(String, int, TemplateOptions) and ComputeService.createNodesInGroup(String, int, TemplateOptions) operations on the Abiquo provider.
